      "text": "おはよう\n挨拶は息を整えてからでいいよ",
      "startTime": 20.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_01-mna002.m4a",
      "text": "今日は油断して二度寝しちゃった～\n琴乃もお母さんも、起こしてくれないんだもん",
      "startTime": 26.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 30.6333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_01-mna003.m4a",
      "text": "まぁ、朝からのダッシュで\nいい運動にはなったけどね",
      "startTime": 33.03333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 35.3666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "だいぶ疲れてるみたいだな\nやっぱり、最近仕事入れ過ぎじゃないのか",
      "startTime": 38.233333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "少し減らすか？\n体を壊したら元も子もないし……",
      "startTime": 43.13333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 45.63333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_01-mna004.m4a",
      "text": "何言ってるの、デビューしたばかりの新人アイドルが\n忙しいなんてありがたいことじゃん",
      "startTime": 49,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_01-mna005.m4a",
      "text": "もっと入れたいぐらいだよ\n本当はこうして授業に出る時間も惜しいくらい",
      "startTime": 53.46666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 56.7333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "俺も麻奈も学業優先だ\n三枝さんもそう言ってただろう？",
      "startTime": 59.43333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    }
